    <text id="A1423T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Hite writes to a cousin, reporting his health and news from home. He requests
                    monetary aid from his cousin.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1864-05-30">May 30<hi rend="underline">
                                <hi rend="super">th</hi>
                        </hi> 1864</date>
                        <name type="place"><orig reg="Prisoners'">Prisoners</orig> Camp <orig
                            reg="Point Lookout">Pointlookout</orig>
                            <abbr expan="Maryland">M<hi rend="underline">
                                <hi rend="super">d</hi>
                            </hi></abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Cousin</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I take this opportunity to write to you a few lines You let you know that I am in
                        <orig reg="tolerable">tolerbly</orig> health at this time and hope that
                    those few lines may find you all enjoying good health all the folks at home were
                    well the last I <orig reg="heard">herd</orig> of your fathers family was all
                    well the last time I <orig reg="heard">herd</orig> from home It has <orig
                        reg="been">bin</orig> a long time since I have <orig reg="heard">herd</orig>
                    from you I would be very glad to hear from you and you may have a very good idea
                    of my situation at this time and would be very much benefited by you if you be
                    so kind as to send me some money as I am in want of some assistance at the <orig
                        reg="present">preasant</orig> time and shall be more than obliged to you I
                    will have to close this as I have not room to write you more. <orig reg="Please"
                        >pleas</orig> write to me soon and direct to me prisoner of war com-I. 10
                        <hi rend="super">
                        <hi rend="underline">th</hi>
                    </hi> division <orig reg="Point Lookout">point lookout</orig> Maryland. In care
                    of Major Weymoth.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Yours most truly</salute>
                    <signed>John N. Hite</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
